{"tid":776493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"西鐵線靈異經歷，想知有冇人有相似經歷","createTime":"2018-08-12T06:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T22:18:02.000Z","uid":113923,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d444a11bdab8c37c99ddc26c7140f768630f5b8c","tid":776493,"uid":113923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:40:25.000Z","msg":"之前返英x學校，要係南昌站落車，嗰時仲未有紅磡站<br />\n當時係朝早返學時間，架車都多人<br />\n由於我係尾站上車，所以我一上車就閉目養神<br />\n到我醒返我發現車廂燈變到好暗，見到出面寫住係美孚，跟住部車就開始入隧道，車廂變得更暗，我唔知點解又瞓返<br />\n再醒返，居然發現出面係荃灣西站，嚇到我成個人即刻醒哂，衝落車，搭咗下一班車返學<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人搭鐵有相似經歷？"},{"pid":"626ed036ac4b926a5476fb8c9dedf76736e8a9f4","tid":776493,"uid":113923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6498d02c3ccf7a246aa2bfa5c21f6b2ec40cf536","tid":776493,"uid":113923,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:08:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fef96ccc93cd08ed36232c5e34c1107f1a3dfb15","tid":776493,"uid":113923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:08:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7a85234da1e0230facee24fdc2e87177b3e8a0b","tid":776493,"uid":113923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f0cd6a061de761a81bf794f2e1dce0d2c2ccfe","tid":776493,"uid":195350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:13:15.000Z","msg":"睇下精神科好wo"},{"pid":"86a82217c25274ff012ca5b57cdcba0d6a330c2c","tid":776493,"uid":46135,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"c